quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  21,51,"Dhugumatti, Nuti kana duras qajeelfama Ibraahiimiif kenninee jirraNuti isa beekoo taanee jirra"
  21,52,Yeroo inni abbaafi ummata isaatiin “Siidaawwan isin (Ibaadaaf) ishee irra teessan kun maali?” jedhe (kennineef)
  21,53,"[Isaan] ni jedhan: “Abbootii keenya kan ishee gabbaran agarre.”"
  21,54,"[Inni] ni jedhe: “Dhugumatti, isiniifi abbootiin keessanis jallina ifa bahaa keessa jirtan.”"
  21,55,"[Isaan] ni jedhaniin: “Sila dhugaan nutti dhufte moo ati warra taphatan irraayi?”"
  21,56,"Ni jedhe: “Baraa, Rabbiin keessan Gooftaa samiifi dachii, kan isaan uume saniAnis kana irratti warra ragaa ba’an irraa tokko.”"
  21,57,"“Allaah’n kakadhee! Ani erga isin dugda gara galtanii deemtan booda dhugumatti, tooftaan ittiin taabota keessan (mancaasun) qopheeffadha” (of keessatti jedhe)"
  21,58,Akka isaan gara isaa (taabota guddichaa) deebi'aniif jecha guddaa isaaniif ta’e tokko qofa (dhiisee) caccabaa isaan godhe
  21,59,"(Isaan) ni jedhan: “Namni gabbaramtoota keenyatti kana hojjate dhugumatti, inni miidhaa raawwattoota irraayi.”"
  21,60,“Dargaggeessa Ibraahiim isaan jedhamu tokko kan maqaa isaanii (hamtuun) dubbatu dhageenyeerra” jedhan
  21,61,"Ni jedhan: “Akka isaan ragaa irratti bahaniif jecha ija namootaa dura fidaa.”"
  21,62,“Sila situ gabbaramtoota keenya irratti (yakka) kana raawwatee Yaa Ibraahiim?” jedhan
  21,63,"(Ibraahiimis) “Lakkii, guddaa isaaniitu kana hojjateYoo kan dubbatan ta’aniif isaan gaafadhaa” jedhe"
  21,64,Gara lubbuu isaanii deebi’anii “isin isinumatu miidhaa raawwattoota” jedhan
  21,65,"Sana booda mataa isaanii lafatti gadi deebisanii “ati dhugumatti, isaan kun hin dubbatanuu beektee jirta (maaliif kana jetta?)” jedhan"
  21,66,"(Ibraahiim) ni jedhe: “Sila Rabbiin ala waan homaa isin hin fayyadneefi isin hin miine gabbartuu"
  21,67,Isiniifi wantoota isin Allaah’n ala gabbartaniinis ‘uffi’ (jedheera)! Sila hin xiinxaltanuu?”
  21,68,"Ni jedhan: “Yoo kan hojjattan taataniif isa gubaa; gabbaramtoota keessanis gargaaraa.”"
  21,69,"Nutis “Yaa ibiddaa! Ibraahiim irratti qabbanaafi nagaa ta’i\" jenne"
  21,70,Isaanis hamtuu itti yaadanNuti isaanuma irra hoonga’oo goone
  21,71,Isaafi Luuxiin gara dachii ishee keessa aalama hundaaf barakaa gooneetti bilisa baafne
  21,72,"Isihaaqiin isaaf kenninee, Ya’aquubis dabalataan (isaaf kennine)Hundaayyuu gaggaarii goone"
  21,73,"Imaamota ajaja keenyaan qajeelchan isaan taasifnee jirraWantoota gaggaarii hojjachuu, salaata dhaabuufi zakaa baafachuus gara isaanitti wahyii gooneWarra Numa (qofa) gabbaran turan"
  21,74,"Luuxiinis murtii haqaafi beekumsa (amantii) isaaf kenninee jirra(Ummata) ganda badii fokkatoo ta’an hojjatan san irraas isa baraarsinee jirraDhugumatti, isaan ummata badoo, finciltoota turan"
  21,75,"Rahmata keenya keessas isa seensifneDhugumatti, inni warra gaggaarii irraayi"